Package org.atlanmod.commons.log

Class Log

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.atlanmod.commons.log.Log
  • @ThreadSafe
@ParametersAreNullableByDefault
public final class Log
extends Object
    The factory that creates Logger instances.

    It also provides static methods for logging without declaring a specific instance. In this case, the root logger is used by default.
